      "raw_text": "The Washington Water Power\nCo. today granted the men who\nwould remain with them and not\njoin the strikers a raise of cents\nan hour, making a wage OF n cents\nan hour for new men. This action\nfollowed conference between\nofficials at which it was stated that\nat the rate the striking carmen\nwere gaining recruits the company\nwas being cramped for enough men\nto maintain its service as it has\nbeen in the past.\n\n\nHeretofore the company has paid\nbut % cents an hour to men who\nhave served less than five years.\nThe increase is made on the five\nyear basis. The strikers consider\nthe company's action as indica-\ntive of the effect of their enroll\nment of recruits has had."
